{
  "version": 1,
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "s0",
      "text": "Giveth Is Present Tense.",
      "start": 0,
      "end": 1.753,
      "scope": "intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "text": "Paul writes one verb at the end of First Corinthians 15 that changes the timeline of every fear you carry.",
      "start": 1.927,
      "end": 8.092,
      "scope": "intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "text": "He says giveth.",
      "start": 8.336,
      "end": 9.601,
      "scope": "intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "text": "Not will give.",
      "start": 9.776,
      "end": 10.739,
      "scope": "intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "text": "Now.",
      "start": 11.064,
      "end": 11.622,
      "scope": "intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "text": "O death, where is thy sting?",
      "start": 11.796,
      "end": 14.164,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "text": "O grave, where is thy victory?",
      "start": 14.373,
      "end": 16.649,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "text": ".",
      "start": 16.649,
      "end": 16.672,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "text": ".",
      "start": 16.672,
      "end": 16.707,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "text": ".",
      "start": 16.707,
      "end": 16.73,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "text": "Thanks be to God, which giveth us the victory through our Lord Jesus Christ.",
      "start": 16.974,
      "end": 21.571,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "text": "-- 1 Corinthians 15:55, 57 (KJV) Paul writes one verb at the end of First Corinthians 15 that changes the timeline of every fear you carry.",
      "start": 21.85,
      "end": 32.624,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "text": "He does not say will give.",
      "start": 33.007,
      "end": 34.493,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "text": "He does not say gave once, long ago.",
      "start": 34.818,
      "end": 36.978,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "text": "He says giveth.",
      "start": 37.221,
      "end": 38.336,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "text": "Present tense.",
      "start": 38.452,
      "end": 39.346,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "text": "Right now, through Jesus, the victory is being handed to you.",
      "start": 39.671,
      "end": 42.678,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "text": "That is the whole reason he taunts death in the same paragraph.",
      "start": 42.957,
      "end": 46.103,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "text": "O death, where is thy sting?",
      "start": 46.428,
      "end": 48.135,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "text": "O grave, where is thy victory?",
      "start": 48.378,
      "end": 50.294,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "text": "He is not bracing for a future fight.",
      "start": 50.467999999999996,
      "end": 52.419,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "text": "He is celebrating a battle that was settled when the stone rolled away, with the receipts being delivered every morning since.",
      "start": 52.663,
      "end": 58.607,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "text": "The Sting Was Pulled A bee can sting once.",
      "start": 58.815999999999995,
      "end": 61.718,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "text": "Then it is finished.",
      "start": 61.892,
      "end": 62.937000000000005,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "text": "Paul is reaching for that picture when he names the sting of death.",
      "start": 63.32,
      "end": 66.304,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "text": "The cross took the sting.",
      "start": 66.513,
      "end": 67.848,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "text": "The tomb confirmed it.",
      "start": 68.092,
      "end": 69.381,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "text": "Death may still come for the body, but it cannot wound the soul of a person who trusts in the risen Christ.",
      "start": 69.706,
      "end": 75.163,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s28",
      "text": "That does not mean grief is unreal.",
      "start": 75.406,
      "end": 77.241,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s29",
      "text": "It does not mean a funeral feels light or a diagnosis hurts less.",
      "start": 77.415,
      "end": 81.362,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s30",
      "text": "It means that none of those is final.",
      "start": 81.745,
      "end": 83.777,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s31",
      "text": "Loss does not have the last say over a child of God.",
      "start": 84.021,
      "end": 87.051,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s32",
      "text": "Death itself is something Paul mocks now, the way you mock a beaten opponent who is still talking.",
      "start": 87.376,
      "end": 93.03,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s33",
      "text": "Victory In the Tense You Live In Most of us are good at past-tense faith, the one that remembers He rose and saved.",
      "start": 93.727,
      "end": 102.841,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s34",
      "text": "We are also good at future-tense faith, the one that trusts He will come back and heaven is real.",
      "start": 103.22399999999999,
      "end": 109.389,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s35",
      "text": "Present-tense faith is the hard one.",
      "start": 109.714,
      "end": 112.11699999999999,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s36",
      "text": "Giveth us the victory.",
      "start": 112.49999999999999,
      "end": 113.963,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s37",
      "text": "Today.",
      "start": 114.24199999999999,
      "end": 114.90299999999999,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s38",
      "text": "This hour.",
      "start": 115.07799999999999,
      "end": 115.821,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s39",
      "text": "In this fear.",
      "start": 115.99499999999999,
      "end": 117.08599999999998,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s40",
      "text": "The resurrection is not a memory you observe once a year.",
      "start": 117.41099999999999,
      "end": 120.84799999999998,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s41",
      "text": "It is a current account you can draw from this morning.",
      "start": 121.09199999999998,
      "end": 123.98299999999999,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s42",
      "text": "What sting are you carrying that Paul would already be taunting?",
      "start": 124.261,
      "end": 127.442,
      "scope": "body"
    },
    {
      "id": "s43",
      "text": "Walk into the day He is already winning.",
      "start": 127.72099999999999,
      "end": 130.49599999999998,
      "scope": "body"
    }
  ]
}